title: Take a Shot ( Front Page News, Rumor Report and Chris Brickley Interview)
itunes:title: Take a Shot ( Front Page News, Rumor Report and Chris Brickley Interview)
description:
Today on the show, after Angela reported on different headlines for Front Page News, and her "Rumor Report, they had trainer Chris Brickley stop by where he spoke about reworking J. Cole's jump shot, relationship with NBA teams, music endeavors and  more. Make sure you check out the next part and hear how Angela helped fix someone's life for "Ask Yee".

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
